Journey: "Checking a box"

    go to "https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/checkboxes"
    check "input[type='checkbox']:nth-of-type(1)"
    "input[type='checkbox']:nth-of-type(1)" should be checked

Journey: "Unchecking a box"

    go to "https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/checkboxes"
    uncheck "input[type='checkbox']:nth-of-type(2)"
    "input[type='checkbox']:nth-of-type(2)" should not be checked
